description: Retrieves information about your channel's schedule.

parameters.name: ChannelName
parameters.description: The name of the channel associated with this Channel Schedule.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: (Optional) If the playback configuration has more than MaxResults channel schedules, use NextToken to get the second and subsequent pages of results. For the first GetChannelScheduleRequest request, omit this value. For the second and subsequent requests, get the value of NextToken from the previous response and specify that value for NextToken in the request. If the previous response didn't include a NextToken element, there are no more channel schedules to get.

nested_items.name: Items
nested_items.description: A list of schedule entries for the channel.

nested_items.name: ApproximateDurationSeconds
nested_items.description: The approximate duration of this program, in seconds.

nested_items.name: ApproximateStartTime
nested_items.description: The approximate time that the program will start playing.

nested_items.name: ChannelName
nested_items.description: The name of the channel that uses this schedule.

nested_items.name: LiveSourceName
nested_items.description: The name of the live source used for the program.

nested_items.name: ApproximateDurationSeconds
nested_items.description: The approximate duration of the ad break, in seconds.

nested_items.name: ApproximateStartTime
nested_items.description: The approximate time that the ad will start playing.

nested_items.name: SourceLocationName
nested_items.description: The name of the source location containing the VOD source used for the ad break.

nested_items.name: VodSourceName
nested_items.description: The name of the VOD source used for the ad break.

nested_items.name: SourceLocationName
nested_items.description: The name of the source location.

nested_items.name: VodSourceName
nested_items.description: The name of the VOD source.

nested_items.name: Audiences
nested_items.description: The list of audiences defined in ScheduleEntry.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: Pagination token returned by the list request when results exceed the maximum allowed. Use the token to fetch the next page of results.
